title: Clash Royale: Enter the EXECUTIONER'S KITCHEN! 🔪🌶️ (New Season! Balance Changes!)
author: Clash Royale
description:
#clashroyale #Executioner
Things are about to heat up with a brand NEW SEASON!
Welcome to the Executioner’s Kitchen!

Season Ingredients:
New Arena: Executioner's Kitchen!
FREE Rare Book of Cards on the Pass Royale free track!
Spicy Balance Changes!
First Executioner Emotes!
New Tower Skin!

See you in the Arena!

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles! From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND PRECISION
Choose Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle! 
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match where anything can happen. 

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

MAKE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal vanity items like Tower Skins and Emotes with the Season Pass and participate in unique in-game events!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards! 

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you do not want to use this feature, please set up password protection for purchases in the settings of your Google Play Store app. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale.
 
A network connection is also required.
 
Support
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or http://supr.cl/ClashRoyaleForum or contact us in game by going to Settings - Help and Support.
